This repository contains educational reports, metadata, workflow descriptions and processed tabular outputs. Unless otherwise stated, these materials are released under the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License.

You are free to share and adapt the material, provided that appropriate credit is given.

This repository does not provide clinical diagnostic advice. The analysis is educational and reproducibility-oriented. Raw public sequencing data remain available from their original public repositories and are subject to the terms of those repositories.
